DatasetsÂ¶

The following datasets were used to power LinkedOut:

  1. Education Data - Covers trends and projections for 2019-2029 and 2023-2033.

  2. Occupation Data - Includes employment statistics and predictions for 2019-2029 and 2023-2033.

  3. Industry Data - Analyzes trends across broad industry sectors.

  4. Labor Force Data - Tracks workforce distribution and changes over time.

  5. Custom User and Job Datasets - Created manually to simulate real-world job seeker scenarios.
